snippet.title: Diana and Roma Learn About Different  Professions in KidZania Dubai
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma visit the play place to learn about different professions. KidZania, a children's city of professions, is located on the territory of the Dubai Mall (Dubai). Here Roma and Diana were able to try themselves in different professions, earn local currency and spend it on entertainment. Learn about different jobs for children with Diana and Roma.
Thanks for watching!
